After the divination, {{ill|Ichishi no Nagaochi|ja|ňŞéšú»ÚĽĚň░żňŞé}}, a descendant of {{ill|Shinetsuhiko|ja|ŠĄÄŠá╣Š┤ąňŻŽ}} would conduct the rites pertaining to Okunitama, replacing the emaciated Nunaki-iri-hime.<ref name="Ellwood-19902" /> {{ill|Ichishi no Nagaochi|ja|ňŞéšú»ÚĽĚň░żňŞé}} would be the ancestor of the Yamato no Kuni no Miyatsuko.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Page:Nihongi by Aston.djvu/208|url=https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Page:Nihongi_by_Aston.djvu/208|access-date=2023-10-24|website=en.wikisource.org|language=en}}</ref>
